 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;i. &quot;">
      An open immersion is étale.
    </html:li>

    
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;ii. &quot;">
      The composition of two étale morphisms is étale.
    </html:li>

    
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;iii. &quot;">
      The base extension of an étale morphism is étale.
    </html:li>

  </html:ol>

  
    
